This is a map from Soldier Of Fortune 2 (Demo Version) game called: mp_shop and made into css.
Maximum Players: 64
Gametypes: All (Bomb/Defuse, Hostage/Rescue, DeathMatch + Others)

Map with 2 Floors: Roof side (boxes, helipad + structures), stairs acess, down part (conference room, kitchen, main halls, elevators, patio, office rooms)
